OL,3,CProgramme listings for TUE 5 MAY
OL,4,G2305FKingdom
OL,5,     GFour rival families - leopards,
OL,6,     Ghyena, wild dogs and lions - all
OL,7,     Gtry to claim a rich corner of
OL,8,     GZambian paradise as their home.
OL,9,     GWho will succeed in ruling this
OL,10,     Gprecious kingdom?
OL,11,G2355FDynasties
OL,12,     GDocumentary following endangered
OL,13,     Gspecies fighting for their
OL,14,     Gsurvival. David, a chimpanzee in
OL,15,     GSenegal, tries to overcome
OL,16,     Gthreats to his leadership and
OL,17,     Gensure an heir.
OL,18,G0055FDynasties II
OL,19,     GIn the wild Patagonian mountains,
OL,20,     Ga puma battles to raise her
OL,21,     Gbiggest litter yet.
