OL,4,G0155FThe Green Planet
OL,5,     GTropical rainforests are plant
OL,6,     Gbattlegrounds. New filming
OL,7,     Gtechniques allow us to enter the
OL,8,     Gworld of plants to see it from
OL,9,     Gtheir perspective and on their
OL,10,     Gtimescale.
OL,11,G0255FMammals
OL,12,     GThe dark, a world of opportunity
OL,13,     Gfor mammals. More than two-thirds
OL,14,     Gprefer the cover of the night,
OL,15,     Gwith some now returning to the
OL,16,     Gsafety of the shadows in order to
OL,17,     Gavoid us.
